OL,6,FAnd NIESR predicts the won't return to
OL,7,Fpre-Covid levels until the end of 2027.
OL,9,FThe brunt of the financial burden has
OL,10,Fbeen felt by the poorest households,
OL,11,FAdrian Pabst, Deputy Director of
OL,12,FNIESR, told ITV News
OL,14,F"The brunt of the hit has fallen on
OL,15,Fthe poorest 50%," says Adrian Pabst,
OL,16,FDeputy Director of NIESR.
