OL,6,FAccording to NIESR, the fall in "real"
OL,7,F(adjusted for inflation) post-tax,
OL,8,Fdisposable incomes of the poorest 10%
OL,9,Fof UK households since 2019/20 amounts
OL,10,Fto approximately #4,500 a year (in
