OL,6,FNIESR's analysis supports the prime
OL,7,Fminister's view, articulated
OL,8,Fyesterday, that the financial pressure
OL,9,Fon households is "starting to ease" as
OL,10,Fenergy bills and mortgage rates fall.
OL,11,FBut it also highlights the
OL,12,Fdifficulties that many households
OL,13,Fstill face.
OL,15,FThis month, eight million people on
OL,16,Fmeans-tested benefits will receive
OL,17,Ftheir final cost-of-living payments,
OL,18,Fas the last of the temporary,
OL,19,F"emergency" taxpayer support falls
OL,20,Faway.
