OL,6,FThe chancellor has already made it
OL,7,Fclear that he would like to cut taxes.
OL,9,FLike the International Monetary Fund
OL,10,F(IMF), NIESR takes the view that there
OL,11,Fare more urgent priorities, but it
OL,12,Fsays that if Jeremy Hunt is determined
OL,13,Fto proceed then he should be lowering
OL,14,Fthe tax burden for those who are most
OL,15,Fin need of support.
OL,17,F"The chancellor should not be
OL,18,Fabolishing inheritance tax, and
OL,19,Fbecause that helps high income
OL,20,Fhouseholds much more than the low
OL,21,Fincome households," says Mr Pabst.
