OL,6,F"To help those in the bottom half of
OL,7,Fthe income distribution, the best
OL,8,Fthing to do is to raise the income tax
OL,9,Fthreshold (from #12,275) because that
OL,10,Fmeans you start paying tax later and
OL,11,Fyou keep more of your own money."
OL,13,FWhatever happens in the Budget, there
OL,14,Fis no quick fix for the UK's economic
OL,15,Fproblems, which pre-date the arrival
OL,16,Fof Covid in 2020.
OL,18,FThe main issue is that for the best
OL,19,Fpart of a generation, Britain's
OL,20,Feconomy has been struck in a low-
OL,21,Fgrowth rut.
