OL,6,FEconomic growth makes everything feel
OL,7,Fbetter: unemployment falls, government
OL,8,Fdebt becomes more sustainable, money
OL,9,Fis freed up to fund public services
OL,10,Fand, most importantly, living
OL,11,Fstandards rise.
OL,13,FProductivity is the Holy Grail. To
OL,14,Fraise growth, and with it , we need to
OL,15,Ffind a way of working more
OL,16,Fefficiently, of increasing the amount
OL,17,Fof goods and services the typical
OL,18,FBritish worker produces each hour.
