OL,6,FNo political parties have explained
OL,7,Fhow they will increase productivity,
OL,8,FMr Pabst said
OL,10,FAn election looms, but Mr Pabst says
OL,11,Fnone of the main political parties
OL,12,Fhave a compelling strategy to revive
OL,13,Fproductivity and with it our
OL,14,Fprosperity.
OL,16,F"(All politicians are) committed to
OL,17,Fhigher growth. Everyone wants to
OL,18,Fincrease productivity. No one has told
OL,19,Fus how to do it," Pabst told ITV News.
